LANDOVER HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION, INC.
v.
SANDERS, et al. No. 13P16-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 13, 2016. Nelson G. Harris, Raleigh, for Landover Homeowners Association, Inc. Matthew D. Quinn, Raleigh, for Sanders, Thomas B., et al.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th of January 2016 by Defendants for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Dissolved by order of the Court in conference, this the 13th of April 2016."
